headline: Equifax Assists Regulated Businesses with AML Compliance
summary: Equifax® (NYSE: EFX) is assisting regulated businesses with the introduction of new AML Compliance Solutions designed to ease the burden of AML (anti-money laundering) regulatory compliance for financial services firms and related industries by flagging potential associations between a prospect and activities that may indicate potential money laundering.
